==English==
===Verb===
'''to [[beat]] [[around]] [[the]] [[bush]]'''
# To [[treat]] a topic but [[omit]] its main [[points]], often intentionally, e.g. because one wants to avoid the main points altogether, but also unintentionally, e.g. by just not being aware of it.
#:''Please stop '''beating around the bush''' and tell me what the problem is!''
